      "message": "Don\u0027t need to inline these; maker_internal is just long enough not to inline.\n\n    struct String {\n        const char* fPtr;\n        bool operator\u003d\u003d(const String\u0026 that) const;\n    };\n    struct Hasher {\n        uint32_t operator()(String k) const;\n    };\n    mutable SkMutex fMutex;\n    SkTHashMap\u003cString, SkString, Hasher\u003e fMap;\n    const SkString\u0026 maker_internal(const char* str);",
      "revId": "8c1efc4053cd631512b31ee8fdcd7eb9d67679b0",
